Package: pulldb
Version: 1.0.1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: PestRoutes Engineering <engineering@pestroutes.com>
Pre-Depends: software-properties-common
Depends: systemd, adduser, bash, zstd, default-mysql-client | mysql-client
Homepage: https://github.com/CharlesHandshy/pullDB
Description: pullDB database restore tooling
 pullDB retrieves production backups and restores them into development
 environments. This package installs the system scaffolding, service
 templates, and installer used to configure the worker daemon.
 .
 Python 3.12 is automatically installed from deadsnakes PPA during setup.
 Fresh installations automatically create the database schema and an
 initial admin user with a randomly generated password.
